				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">This trick was mentioned in the old Allegro documentation: to convert signed samples to unsigned, you just had to flip the MSB. What this does is shift the range (so e.g. -0x80~0x7F gets shifted to 0x00~0xFF - it's equivalent to adding 0x80 to all values).</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

						<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
						<tr valign="middle">
							<td class="gensmall" align="right">
							
